            <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Se ha agregado un nuevo informe en el sistema</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email_message" style="margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #424242; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; padding: 10px 30px;">
            hello <%= name %>: <br> <br>
           Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quos quisquam incidunt sequi unde delectus fugiat veniam inventore dignissimos est aut laudantium beatae minus sapiente odio aperiam mollitia, accusamus maiores illo.
        </div>
        <div class="table-container" style="padding: 0px 30px; text-align: left;">
            <table class="desktop-table">
                <tr>
                    <td style="min-width:160px; background-color: #F5F5F5; padding: 10px 16px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing ?:</td>
                    <td style="width: 100%; padding: 10px 16px;"><%= report_id %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table class="mobile-table">
                <tr>
                    <td style="min-width:160px; background-color: #F5F5F5; padding: 10px 16px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet cons, quo ratione :</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%; padding: 10px 16px;"><%= report_id %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="email_footer" style="color:  #616161; text-align: left; font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 30px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                <p style="font-family: 'Open Sans';font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 600; color: #424242;">Lorem ipsum dolor  :</p>
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.: <a href="<%= url %>?report_id=<%= report_id %>" target="_blank" style="color:#01579B; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= url %>?report_id=<%= report_id %></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr style="border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0; margin:10px 24px;">
        <div class="email_footer" style="padding: 0px 30px; color:  #616161; text-align: left; font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
           Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aliquid, eum.
            <a href="mailto:canal.informacion@uneatlantico.es" style="color:#01579B; text-decoration: none;">canal.informacion@uneatlantico.es.</a>
            <br>
            Un saludo.
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center;font-family: 'Open Sans';font-size: 12px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400; color: #616161;">
            <p>Ha recibido este correo porque se encuentra dado de alta en</p>
            <p style="color: #01579B;">Canal Ético UNEATLANTICO</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
